snippet.title: Finding Paradise - Music & Screenshots Teaser
snippet.description:
Steam page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/337340/Finding_Paradise/

Releases December 14, 2017

"Finding Paradise" is the second installment of Sigmund Corp. series, following "To the Moon" (trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sqkJuSV-23U )

Like its predecessor, it features a standalone story following two doctors as they traverse through a dying patient's memories to artificially fulfill their last wish.

---------------------------------------
Music in the video:
---------------------------------------
"Time is a Place"
Finding Paradise OST 
Composed by: Kan Gao
---------------------------------------
